   In particular, it is intended to solve the problem of a newly completed
   wind power generator that makes it very difficult to predict the amount
   of electricity generated due to the lack of data on past power
   generation. To this end, a deep learning based transfer learning model
   was proposed and compared with other models, such as a deep learning
   model without transfer learning and Light Gradient Boosting Machine
