Abstract = {The world energy structure dominated by fossil energy has brought about
   the depletion of fossil energy and a series of environmental pollution
   problems. The development of new energy has become the direction of
   joint efforts of China and other countries in the world. Wind energy is
   an important part of new energies. Accurate wind speed prediction can
   effectively reduce the adverse impact of wind farm fluctuation on power
   system. To solve the problem of low and poor accuracy of short-term wind
   speed prediction, a hybrid prediction model based on improved optimized
   extreme learning machine (ELM) is provided in this paper. The wind speed
