   long short-term memory network's hyperparameters may affect the
   prediction results, In the present study, a hybrid prediction model
   based on the long short-term memory and the modified tuna swarm
   optimization algorithm was established, and was used to predict after
   the wind speed sample data had been decomposed by successive variational
   mode decomposition method. The experimental results reveal that the
   proposed model effectively improved the accuracy of wind speed
