   irradiance, ambient temperature, and wind speed) and corresponding
   solutions have not been thoroughly investigated. In this paper, a new
   energy management systems (EMS) based on weather and load forecasting is
   proposed for PMG's optimal scheduling and operation. Developing a novel
   hybrid machine learning-based method using adaptive neuro-fuzzy
   inference system (ANFIS), multilayer perceptron (MLP) artificial neural
   network (ANN), and radial basis function (RBF) ANN to precisely predict
   the load and weather data is one of the most important contributions of
